{
  "stem": "13382.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So it was-- so I can say it was a love affair.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in a different way, like this, today's.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because just before my mother passed away, she showed me a bundle of letters, which was-- there was a pink ribbon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they were the love letters which my father was writing to her.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was something, you know, which it's so good to remember.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because this is all emotion.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is all genuine.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is sort of-- they're very close to my heart.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my father got married.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And obviously, with marriage, dowry comes as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because he-- he didn't have any money.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And my mother's family was reasonably set up.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So as they were-- I think they divide it somehow, how the dowry went, with so many children and so much they've got.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So when the first daughter or any daughter leaves, they get their part.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then everything is settled.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And should the time come that the parents are retiring or they pass away, so the other-- other part as left with the boys.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my mother really was paid out this way.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "As a dowry.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 57,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As a dowry, right?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they went back to my father's place where we lived, in Fil'akovo.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And as my father had no profession, they opened a haberdashery shop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they managed it quite well and-- till the Depression came.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was already three children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was Alex, my eldest brother, Edith, my sister, and myself.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Father went to buy goods in the normal way because he knew so much goods will be sort of sold.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when he came home, I mean, the situation became worse.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they got a quite difficult financial squeeze.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
